column6: Marvel's Mightiest Women finally get their own explosive series! In a secluded corner of the Battleworld, an island nation is fiercely protected by a team of Avengers the likes of which has only ever been glimpsed before... Fighting to protect the small sliver of their world that's left, the Amazing A-FORCE stands shoulder-to-shoulder, ready to take on the horde!
column8: | writer:Marguerite Bennett | writer:G. Willow Wilson | penciller (cover):Jim Cheung | artist:Jorge Molina
